Opinion WHAT HAVE THEY FOUND? Christopher Halliwell detectives remove wheelie bins plastered with biohazard stickers as they dig up garden in search for more bodies 
Neighbours could hear power tools coming from inside the double murderer's garage as cops say he may be linked to missing Claudia Lawrence By GEMMA MULLIN, GUY BIRCHALL AND HOLLY CHRISTODOULOU 21st February 2017, 5:40 pm
